name: equalpunks
description:
=Dao is a Social Experiment DAO that merges DEFI with NFT's, All Punks are man made 1/1s

Basic DAO structure.

1.All =dao sales are converted to $EQUAL and added to the DAO veEQUAL NFT
2.=dao holders are verified by NFT ownership and added to a private discord channel by role, where voting strategies can be discussed.
3.Voting weight will be decided by # of =daos held.
4.Votes will be distributed to 3 Seperate pairs based on weight, overall % will be discussed by the =dao (33% each, 70/20/10 etc)
5.80% of Fees earned from voting will be used to add more veEQUAL, 20% will go to the Creator Treasury.

This Project aims to explore the possibilities of the ve(3,3) model through community building whilst supporting the growth of the Equalizer Protocol.
